1.  I Have write main.tf file to create 2 ec2 instances in two different rigions 

2.  While writing the mai.tf file, I used Userdate funtion to perform commands which install nginx at time of launch

3.  this file give us IP address as a output of this two ec2 instances 

4. using that ip, we can access port 80 to access nginx server

terraform commands performed
  1.  terraform init
  2.  terraform validate
  3.  terraform plan
  4.  terraform apply

also I have connected my aws account to terraform at start using "aws configure" command and provided access key to access account 

